var book = {
	"name": "Revelation",
	"numChapters": 22,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The revelation from Jesus Christ, which God gave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30699A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30699A\"></sup> him to show his servants what must soon take place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30699B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30699B\"></sup> He made it known by sending his angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30699C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30699C\"></sup> to his servant John,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30699D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30699D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>who testifies to everything he saw—that is, the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30700E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30700E\"></sup> and the testimony of Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30700F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30700F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Blessed is the one who reads aloud the words of this prophecy, and blessed are those who hear it and take to heart what is written in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30701G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30701G\"></sup> because the time is near.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30701H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30701H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>John,To the seven churches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30702I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30702I\"></sup> in the province of Asia:Grace and peace to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30702J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30702J\"></sup> from him who is, and who was, and who is to come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30702K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30702K\"></sup> and from the seven spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30702L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30702L\"></sup> before his throne,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and from Jesus Christ, who is the faithful witness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30703M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30703M\"></sup> the firstborn from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30703N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30703N\"></sup> and the ruler of the kings of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30703O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30703O\"></sup>To him who loves us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30703P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30703P\"></sup> and has freed us from our sins by his blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30703Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30703Q\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and has made us to be a kingdom and priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30704R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30704R\"></sup> to serve his God and Father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30704S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30704S\"></sup>—to him be glory and power for ever and ever! Amen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30704T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30704T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Look, he is coming with the clouds,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30705U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30705U\"></sup>and “every eye will see him,even those who pierced him”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30705V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30705V\"></sup>and all peoples on earth “will mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30705W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30705W\"></sup> because of him.”So shall it be! Amen.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“I am the Alpha and the Omega,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30706X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30706X\"></sup> says the Lord God, “who is, and who was, and who is to come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30706Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30706Y\"></sup> the Almighty.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30706Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30706Z\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I, John,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30707AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30707AA\"></sup> your brother and companion in the suffering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30707AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30707AB\"></sup> and kingdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30707AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30707AC\"></sup> and patient endurance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30707AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30707AD\"></sup> that are ours in Jesus, was on the island of Patmos because of the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30707AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30707AE\"></sup> and the testimony of Jesus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30707AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30707AF\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>On the Lord’s Day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30708AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30708AG\"></sup> I was in the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30708AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30708AH\"></sup> and I heard behind me a loud voice like a trumpet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30708AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30708AI\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>which said: <span class=\"woj\">“Write on a scroll what you see<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AJ\"></sup> and send it to the seven churches:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AK\"></sup> to Ephesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AL\"></sup> Smyrna,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AM\"></sup> Pergamum,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AN\"></sup> Thyatira,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AO\"></sup> Sardis,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AP\"></sup> Philadelphia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AQ\"></sup> and Laodicea.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30709AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30709AR\"></sup></span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I turned around to see the voice that was speaking to me. And when I turned I saw seven golden lampstands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30710AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30710AS\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and among the lampstands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30711AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30711AT\"></sup> was someone like a son of man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30711AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30711AU\"></sup> dressed in a robe reaching down to his feet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30711AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30711AV\"></sup> and with a golden sash around his chest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30711AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30711AW\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The hair on his head was white like wool, as white as snow, and his eyes were like blazing fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30712AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30712AX\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>His feet were like bronze glowing in a furnace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30713AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30713AY\"></sup> and his voice was like the sound of rushing waters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30713AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30713AZ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In his right hand he held seven stars,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30714BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30714BA\"></sup> and coming out of his mouth was a sharp, double-edged sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30714BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30714BB\"></sup> His face was like the sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30714BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30714BC\"></sup> shining in all its brilliance.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When I saw him, I fell at his feet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30715BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30715BD\"></sup> as though dead. Then he placed his right hand on me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30715BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30715BE\"></sup> and said: <span class=\"woj\">“Do not be afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30715BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30715BF\"></sup> I am the First and the Last.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30715BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30715BG\"></sup></span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I am the Living One; I was dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30716BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30716BH\"></sup> and now look, I am alive for ever and ever!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30716BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30716BI\"></sup> And I hold the keys of death and Hades.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30716BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30716BJ\"></sup></span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Write, therefore, what you have seen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30717BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30717BK\"></sup> what is now and what will take place later.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The mystery of the seven stars that you saw in my right hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30718BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30718BL\"></sup> and of the seven golden lampstands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30718BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30718BM\"></sup> is this: The seven stars are the angels of the seven churches,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30718BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30718BN\"></sup> and the seven lampstands are the seven churches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30718BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30718BO\"></sup></span>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span><span class=\"woj\">“To the angel of the church in Ephesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30719A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30719A\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of him who holds the seven stars in his right hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30719B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30719B\"></sup> and walks among the seven golden lampstands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30719C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30719C\"></sup></span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I know your deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30720D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30720D\"></sup> your hard work and your perseverance. I know that you cannot tolerate wicked people, that you have tested<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30720E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30720E\"></sup> those who claim to be apostles but are not, and have found them false.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30720F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30720F\"></sup></span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You have persevered and have endured hardships for my name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30721G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30721G\"></sup> and have not grown weary.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet I hold this against you: You have forsaken the love you had at first.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30722H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30722H\"></sup></span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Consider how far you have fallen! Repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30723I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30723I\"></sup> and do the things you did at first. If you do not repent, I will come to you and remove your lampstand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30723J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30723J\"></sup> from its place.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But you have this in your favor: You hate the practices of the Nicolaitans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30724K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30724K\"></sup> which I also hate.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30725L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30725L\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches. To the one who is victorious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30725M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30725M\"></sup> I will give the right to eat from the tree of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30725N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30725N\"></sup> which is in the paradise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30725O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30725O\"></sup> of God.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“To the angel of the church in Smyrna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30726P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30726P\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of him who is the First and the Last,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30726Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30726Q\"></sup> who died and came to life again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30726R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30726R\"></sup></span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I know your afflictions and your poverty—yet you are rich!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30727S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30727S\"></sup> I know about the slander of those who say they are Jews and are not,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30727T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30727T\"></sup> but are a synagogue of Satan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30727U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30727U\"></sup></span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not be afraid of what you are about to suffer. I tell you, the devil will put some of you in prison to test you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30728V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30728V\"></sup> and you will suffer persecution for ten days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30728W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30728W\"></sup> Be faithful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30728X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30728X\"></sup> even to the point of death, and I will give you life as your victor’s crown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30728Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30728Y\"></sup></span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30729Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30729Z\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches. The one who is victorious will not be hurt at all by the second death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30729AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30729AA\"></sup></span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“To the angel of the church in Pergamum<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30730AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30730AB\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of him who has the sharp, double-edged sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30730AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30730AC\"></sup></span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I know where you live—where Satan has his throne. Yet you remain true to my name. You did not renounce your faith in me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30731AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30731AD\"></sup> not even in the days of Antipas, my faithful witness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30731AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30731AE\"></sup> who was put to death in your city—where Satan lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30731AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30731AF\"></sup></span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Nevertheless, I have a few things against you:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30732AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30732AG\"></sup> There are some among you who hold to the teaching of Balaam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30732AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30732AH\"></sup> who taught Balak to entice the Israelites to sin so that they ate food sacrificed to idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30732AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30732AI\"></sup> and committed sexual immorality.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30732AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30732AJ\"></sup></span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Likewise, you also have those who hold to the teaching of the Nicolaitans.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30733AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30733AK\"></sup></span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30734AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30734AL\"></sup> therefore! Otherwise, I will soon come to you and will fight against them with the sword of my mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30734AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30734AM\"></sup></span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30735AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30735AN\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches. To the one who is victorious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30735AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30735AO\"></sup> I will give some of the hidden manna.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30735AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30735AP\"></sup> I will also give that person a white stone with a new name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30735AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30735AQ\"></sup> written on it, known only to the one who receives it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30735AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30735AR\"></sup></span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“To the angel of the church in Thyatira<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30736AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30736AS\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of the Son of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30736AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30736AT\"></sup> whose eyes are like blazing fire and whose feet are like burnished bronze.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30736AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30736AU\"></sup></span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I know your deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30737AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30737AV\"></sup> your love and faith, your service and perseverance, and that you are now doing more than you did at first.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Nevertheless, I have this against you: You tolerate that woman Jezebel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30738AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30738AW\"></sup> who calls herself a prophet. By her teaching she misleads my servants into sexual immorality and the eating of food sacrificed to idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30738AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30738AX\"></sup></span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I have given her time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30739AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30739AY\"></sup> to repent of her immorality, but she is unwilling.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30739AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30739AZ\"></sup></span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So I will cast her on a bed of suffering, and I will make those who commit adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30740BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30740BA\"></sup> with her suffer intensely, unless they repent of her ways.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will strike her children dead. Then all the churches will know that I am he who searches hearts and minds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30741BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30741BB\"></sup> and I will repay each of you according to your deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30741BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30741BC\"></sup></span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now I say to the rest of you in Thyatira, to you who do not hold to her teaching and have not learned Satan’s so-called deep secrets, ‘I will not impose any other burden on you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30742BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30742BD\"></sup></span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>except to hold on to what you have<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30743BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30743BE\"></sup> until I come.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30743BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30743BF\"></sup></span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>To the one who is victorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30744BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30744BG\"></sup> and does my will to the end,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30744BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30744BH\"></sup> I will give authority over the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30744BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30744BI\"></sup>—</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>that one ‘will rule them with an iron scepter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30745BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30745BJ\"></sup> and will dash them to pieces like pottery’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30745BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30745BK\"></sup>—just as I have received authority from my Father.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I will also give that one the morning star.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30746BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30746BL\"></sup></span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30747BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30747BM\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches.</span>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><span class=\"woj\">“To the angel of the church in Sardis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30748A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30748A\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of him who holds the seven spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30748B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30748B\"></sup> of God and the seven stars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30748C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30748C\"></sup> I know your deeds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30748D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30748D\"></sup> you have a reputation of being alive, but you are dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30748E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30748E\"></sup></span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Wake up! Strengthen what remains and is about to die, for I have found your deeds unfinished in the sight of my God.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Remember, therefore, what you have received and heard; hold it fast, and repent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30750F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30750F\"></sup> But if you do not wake up, I will come like a thief,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30750G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30750G\"></sup> and you will not know at what time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30750H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30750H\"></sup> I will come to you.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet you have a few people in Sardis who have not soiled their clothes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30751I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30751I\"></sup> They will walk with me, dressed in white,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30751J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30751J\"></sup> for they are worthy.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The one who is victorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30752K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30752K\"></sup> will, like them, be dressed in white.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30752L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30752L\"></sup> I will never blot out the name of that person from the book of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30752M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30752M\"></sup> but will acknowledge that name before my Father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30752N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30752N\"></sup> and his angels.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30753O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30753O\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“To the angel of the church in Philadelphia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30754P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30754P\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of him who is holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30754Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30754Q\"></sup> and true,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30754R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30754R\"></sup> who holds the key of David.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30754S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30754S\"></sup> What he opens no one can shut, and what he shuts no one can open.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I know your deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30755T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30755T\"></sup> See, I have placed before you an open door<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30755U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30755U\"></sup> that no one can shut. I know that you have little strength, yet you have kept my word and have not denied my name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30755V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30755V\"></sup></span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make those who are of the synagogue of Satan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30756W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30756W\"></sup> who claim to be Jews though they are not,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30756X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30756X\"></sup> but are liars—I will make them come and fall down at your feet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30756Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30756Y\"></sup> and acknowledge that I have loved you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30756Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30756Z\"></sup></span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Since you have kept my command to endure patiently, I will also keep you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30757AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30757AA\"></sup> from the hour of trial that is going to come on the whole world<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30757AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30757AB\"></sup> to test<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30757AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30757AC\"></sup> the inhabitants of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30757AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30757AD\"></sup></span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I am coming soon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30758AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30758AE\"></sup> Hold on to what you have,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30758AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30758AF\"></sup> so that no one will take your crown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30758AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30758AG\"></sup></span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The one who is victorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30759AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30759AH\"></sup> I will make a pillar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30759AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30759AI\"></sup> in the temple of my God. Never again will they leave it. I will write on them the name of my God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30759AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30759AJ\"></sup> and the name of the city of my God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30759AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30759AK\"></sup> the new Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30759AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30759AL\"></sup> which is coming down out of heaven from my God; and I will also write on them my new name.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30760AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30760AM\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“To the angel of the church in Laodicea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30761AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30761AN\"></sup> write:</span><span class=\"woj\">These are the words of the Amen, the faithful and true witness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30761AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30761AO\"></sup> the ruler of God’s creation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30761AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30761AP\"></sup></span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I know your deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30762AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30762AQ\"></sup> that you are neither cold nor hot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30762AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30762AR\"></sup> I wish you were either one or the other!</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So, because you are lukewarm—neither hot nor cold—I am about to spit you out of my mouth.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You say, ‘I am rich; I have acquired wealth and do not need a thing.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30764AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30764AS\"></sup> But you do not realize that you are wretched, pitiful, poor, blind and naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30764AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30764AT\"></sup></span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I counsel you to buy from me gold refined in the fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30765AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30765AU\"></sup> so you can become rich; and white clothes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30765AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30765AV\"></sup> to wear, so you can cover your shameful nakedness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30765AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30765AW\"></sup> and salve to put on your eyes, so you can see.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Those whom I love I rebuke and discipline.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30766AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30766AX\"></sup> So be earnest and repent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30766AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30766AY\"></sup></span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Here I am! I stand at the door<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30767AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30767AZ\"></sup> and knock. If anyone hears my voice and opens the door,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30767BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30767BA\"></sup> I will come in<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30767BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30767BB\"></sup> and eat with that person, and they with me.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To the one who is victorious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30768BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30768BC\"></sup> I will give the right to sit with me on my throne,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30768BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30768BD\"></sup> just as I was victorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30768BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30768BE\"></sup> and sat down with my Father on his throne.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30769BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30769BF\"></sup> what the Spirit says to the churches.”</span>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>After this I looked, and there before me was a door standing open<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30770A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30770A\"></sup> in heaven. And the voice I had first heard speaking to me like a trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30770B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30770B\"></sup> said, <span class=\"woj\">“Come up here,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30770C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30770C\"></sup> and I will show you what must take place after this.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30770D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30770D\"></sup></span>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>At once I was in the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30771E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30771E\"></sup> and there before me was a throne in heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30771F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30771F\"></sup> with someone sitting on it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the one who sat there had the appearance of jasper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30772G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30772G\"></sup> and ruby.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30772H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30772H\"></sup> A rainbow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30772I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30772I\"></sup> that shone like an emerald<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30772J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30772J\"></sup> encircled the throne.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Surrounding the throne were twenty-four other thrones, and seated on them were twenty-four elders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30773K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30773K\"></sup> They were dressed in white<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30773L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30773L\"></sup> and had crowns of gold on their heads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>From the throne came flashes of lightning, rumblings and peals of thunder.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30774M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30774M\"></sup> In front of the throne, seven lamps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30774N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30774N\"></sup> were blazing. These are the seven spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30774O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30774O\"></sup> of God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Also in front of the throne there was what looked like a sea of glass,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30775P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30775P\"></sup> clear as crystal.In the center, around the throne, were four living creatures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30775Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30775Q\"></sup> and they were covered with eyes, in front and in back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30775R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30775R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The first living creature was like a lion, the second was like an ox, the third had a face like a man, the fourth was like a flying eagle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30776S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30776S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Each of the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30777T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30777T\"></sup> had six wings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30777U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30777U\"></sup> and was covered with eyes all around,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30777V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30777V\"></sup> even under its wings. Day and night<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30777W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30777W\"></sup> they never stop saying:“‘Holy, holy, holyis the Lord God Almighty,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30777X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30777X\"></sup>who was, and is, and is to come.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30777Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30777Y\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whenever the living creatures give glory, honor and thanks to him who sits on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30778Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30778Z\"></sup> and who lives for ever and ever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30778AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30778AA\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>the twenty-four elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30779AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30779AB\"></sup> fall down before him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30779AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30779AC\"></sup> who sits on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30779AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30779AD\"></sup> and worship him who lives for ever and ever. They lay their crowns before the throne and say:",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“You are worthy, our Lord and God,to receive glory and honor and power,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30780AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30780AE\"></sup>for you created all things,and by your will they were createdand have their being.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30780AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30780AF\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Then I saw in the right hand of him who sat on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30781A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30781A\"></sup> a scroll with writing on both sides<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30781B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30781B\"></sup> and sealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30781C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30781C\"></sup> with seven seals.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw a mighty angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30782D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30782D\"></sup> proclaiming in a loud voice, “Who is worthy to break the seals and open the scroll?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But no one in heaven or on earth or under the earth could open the scroll or even look inside it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I wept and wept because no one was found who was worthy to open the scroll or look inside.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then one of the elders said to me, “Do not weep! See, the Lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30785E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30785E\"></sup> of the tribe of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30785F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30785F\"></sup> the Root of David,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30785G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30785G\"></sup> has triumphed. He is able to open the scroll and its seven seals.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I saw a Lamb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30786H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30786H\"></sup> looking as if it had been slain, standing at the center of the throne, encircled by the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30786I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30786I\"></sup> and the elders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30786J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30786J\"></sup> The Lamb had seven horns and seven eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30786K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30786K\"></sup> which are the seven spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30786L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30786L\"></sup> of God sent out into all the earth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He went and took the scroll from the right hand of him who sat on the throne.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30787M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30787M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And when he had taken it, the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30788N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30788N\"></sup> and the twenty-four elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30788O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30788O\"></sup> fell down before the Lamb. Each one had a harp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30788P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30788P\"></sup> and they were holding golden bowls full of incense, which are the prayers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30788Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30788Q\"></sup> of God’s people.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And they sang a new song, saying:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30789R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30789R\"></sup>“You are worthy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30789S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30789S\"></sup> to take the scrolland to open its seals,because you were slain,and with your blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30789T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30789T\"></sup> you purchased<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30789U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30789U\"></sup> for Godpersons from every tribe and language and people and nation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30789V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30789V\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You have made them to be a kingdom and priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30790W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30790W\"></sup> to serve our God,and they will reign on the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30790X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30790X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I looked and heard the voice of many angels, numbering thousands upon thousands, and ten thousand times ten thousand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30791Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30791Y\"></sup> They encircled the throne and the living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30791Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30791Z\"></sup> and the elders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30791AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30791AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In a loud voice they were saying:“Worthy is the Lamb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30792AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30792AB\"></sup> who was slain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30792AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30792AC\"></sup>to receive power and wealth and wisdom and strengthand honor and glory and praise!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30792AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30792AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I heard every creature in heaven and on earth and under the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30793AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30793AE\"></sup> and on the sea, and all that is in them, saying:“To him who sits on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30793AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30793AF\"></sup> and to the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30793AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30793AG\"></sup>be praise and honor and glory and power,for ever and ever!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30793AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30793AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30794AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30794AI\"></sup> said, “Amen,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30794AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30794AJ\"></sup> and the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30794AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30794AK\"></sup> fell down and worshiped.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30794AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30794AL\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>I watched as the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30795A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30795A\"></sup> opened the first of the seven seals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30795B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30795B\"></sup> Then I heard one of the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30795C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30795C\"></sup> say in a voice like thunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30795D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30795D\"></sup> “Come!”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I looked, and there before me was a white horse!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30796E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30796E\"></sup> Its rider held a bow, and he was given a crown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30796F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30796F\"></sup> and he rode out as a conqueror bent on conquest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30796G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30796G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When the Lamb opened the second seal, I heard the second living creature<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30797H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30797H\"></sup> say, “Come!”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then another horse came out, a fiery red one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30798I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30798I\"></sup> Its rider was given power to take peace from the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30798J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30798J\"></sup> and to make people kill each other. To him was given a large sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the Lamb opened the third seal, I heard the third living creature<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30799K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30799K\"></sup> say, “Come!” I looked, and there before me was a black horse!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30799L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30799L\"></sup> Its rider was holding a pair of scales in his hand.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I heard what sounded like a voice among the four living creatures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30800M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30800M\"></sup> saying, “Two pounds of wheat for a day’s wages, and six pounds of barley for a day’s wages,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30800N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30800N\"></sup> and do not damage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30800O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30800O\"></sup> the oil and the wine!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the Lamb opened the fourth seal, I heard the voice of the fourth living creature<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30801P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30801P\"></sup> say, “Come!”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I looked, and there before me was a pale horse!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30802Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30802Q\"></sup> Its rider was named Death, and Hades<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30802R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30802R\"></sup> was following close behind him. They were given power over a fourth of the earth to kill by sword, famine and plague, and by the wild beasts of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30802S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30802S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When he opened the fifth seal, I saw under<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30803T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30803T\"></sup> the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30803U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30803U\"></sup> the souls of those who had been slain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30803V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30803V\"></sup> because of the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30803W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30803W\"></sup> and the testimony they had maintained.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They called out in a loud voice, “How long,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30804X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30804X\"></sup> Sovereign Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30804Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30804Y\"></sup> holy and true,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30804Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30804Z\"></sup> until you judge the inhabitants of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30804AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30804AA\"></sup> and avenge our blood?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30804AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30804AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then each of them was given a white robe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30805AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30805AC\"></sup> and they were told to wait a little longer, until the full number of their fellow servants, their brothers and sisters, were killed just as they had been.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30805AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30805AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I watched as he opened the sixth seal. There was a great earthquake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30806AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30806AE\"></sup> The sun turned black<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30806AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30806AF\"></sup> like sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30806AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30806AG\"></sup> made of goat hair, the whole moon turned blood red,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and the stars in the sky fell to earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30807AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30807AH\"></sup> as figs drop from a fig tree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30807AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30807AI\"></sup> when shaken by a strong wind.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The heavens receded like a scroll being rolled up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30808AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30808AJ\"></sup> and every mountain and island was removed from its place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30808AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30808AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the kings of the earth, the princes, the generals, the rich, the mighty, and everyone else, both slave and free,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30809AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30809AL\"></sup> hid in caves and among the rocks of the mountains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30809AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30809AM\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They called to the mountains and the rocks, “Fall on us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30810AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30810AN\"></sup> and hide us from the face of him who sits on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30810AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30810AO\"></sup> and from the wrath of the Lamb!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For the great day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30811AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30811AP\"></sup> of their wrath has come, and who can withstand it?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30811AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30811AQ\"></sup>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>After this I saw four angels standing at the four corners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30812A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30812A\"></sup> of the earth, holding back the four winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30812B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30812B\"></sup> of the earth to prevent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30812C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30812C\"></sup> any wind from blowing on the land or on the sea or on any tree.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then I saw another angel coming up from the east, having the seal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30813D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30813D\"></sup> of the living God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30813E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30813E\"></sup> He called out in a loud voice to the four angels who had been given power to harm the land and the sea:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30813F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30813F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Do not harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30814G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30814G\"></sup> the land or the sea or the trees until we put a seal on the foreheads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30814H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30814H\"></sup> of the servants of our God.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I heard the number<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30815I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30815I\"></sup> of those who were sealed: 144,000<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30815J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30815J\"></sup> from all the tribes of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>From the tribe of Judah 12,000 were sealed,from the tribe of Reuben 12,000,from the tribe of Gad 12,000,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>from the tribe of Asher 12,000,from the tribe of Naphtali 12,000,from the tribe of Manasseh 12,000,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>from the tribe of Simeon 12,000,from the tribe of Levi 12,000,from the tribe of Issachar 12,000,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>from the tribe of Zebulun 12,000,from the tribe of Joseph 12,000,from the tribe of Benjamin 12,000.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After this I looked, and there before me was a great multitude that no one could count, from every nation, tribe, people and language,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30820K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30820K\"></sup> standing before the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30820L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30820L\"></sup> and before the Lamb. They were wearing white robes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30820M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30820M\"></sup> and were holding palm branches in their hands.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And they cried out in a loud voice:“Salvation belongs to our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30821N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30821N\"></sup>who sits on the throne,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30821O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30821O\"></sup>and to the Lamb.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All the angels were standing around the throne and around the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30822P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30822P\"></sup> and the four living creatures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30822Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30822Q\"></sup> They fell down on their faces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30822R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30822R\"></sup> before the throne and worshiped God,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying:“Amen!Praise and gloryand wisdom and thanks and honorand power and strengthbe to our God for ever and ever.Amen!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30823S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30823S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then one of the elders asked me, “These in white robes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30824T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30824T\"></sup>—who are they, and where did they come from?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I answered, “Sir, you know.”And he said, “These are they who have come out of the great tribulation; they have washed their robes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30825U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30825U\"></sup> and made them white in the blood of the Lamb.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30825V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30825V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore,“they are before the throne of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30826W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30826W\"></sup>and serve him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30826X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30826X\"></sup> day and night in his temple;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30826Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30826Y\"></sup>and he who sits on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30826Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30826Z\"></sup>will shelter them with his presence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30826AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30826AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>‘Never again will they hunger;never again will they thirst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30827AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30827AB\"></sup>The sun will not beat down on them,’nor any scorching heat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30827AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30827AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For the Lamb at the center of the thronewill be their shepherd;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30828AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30828AD\"></sup>‘he will lead them to springs of living water.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30828AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30828AE\"></sup>‘And God will wipe away every tear from their eyes.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30828AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30828AF\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>When he opened the seventh seal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30829A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30829A\"></sup> there was silence in heaven for about half an hour.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw the seven angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30830B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30830B\"></sup> who stand before God, and seven trumpets were given to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30830C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30830C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Another angel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30831D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30831D\"></sup> who had a golden censer, came and stood at the altar. He was given much incense to offer, with the prayers of all God’s people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30831E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30831E\"></sup> on the golden altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30831F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30831F\"></sup> in front of the throne.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The smoke of the incense, together with the prayers of God’s people, went up before God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30832G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30832G\"></sup> from the angel’s hand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel took the censer, filled it with fire from the altar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30833H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30833H\"></sup> and hurled it on the earth; and there came peals of thunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30833I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30833I\"></sup> rumblings, flashes of lightning and an earthquake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30833J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30833J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the seven angels who had the seven trumpets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30834K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30834K\"></sup> prepared to sound them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The first angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30835L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30835L\"></sup> sounded his trumpet, and there came hail and fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30835M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30835M\"></sup> mixed with blood, and it was hurled down on the earth. A third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30835N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30835N\"></sup> of the earth was burned up, a third of the trees were burned up, and all the green grass was burned up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30835O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30835O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The second angel sounded his trumpet, and something like a huge mountain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30836P\"></sup> all ablaze, was thrown into the sea. A third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30836Q\"></sup> of the sea turned into blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30836R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30836R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>a third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30837S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30837S\"></sup> of the living creatures in the sea died, and a third of the ships were destroyed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The third angel sounded his trumpet, and a great star, blazing like a torch, fell from the sky<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30838T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30838T\"></sup> on a third of the rivers and on the springs of water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30838U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30838U\"></sup>—",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>the name of the star is Wormwood. A third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30839V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30839V\"></sup> of the waters turned bitter, and many people died from the waters that had become bitter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30839W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The fourth angel sounded his trumpet, and a third of the sun was struck, a third of the moon, and a third of the stars, so that a third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30840X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30840X\"></sup> of them turned dark.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30840Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30840Y\"></sup> A third of the day was without light, and also a third of the night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30840Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30840Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As I watched, I heard an eagle that was flying in midair<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30841AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30841AA\"></sup> call out in a loud voice: “Woe! Woe! Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30841AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30841AB\"></sup> to the inhabitants of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30841AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30841AC\"></sup> because of the trumpet blasts about to be sounded by the other three angels!”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>The fifth angel sounded his trumpet, and I saw a star that had fallen from the sky to the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30842A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30842A\"></sup> The star was given the key<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30842B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30842B\"></sup> to the shaft of the Abyss.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30842C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30842C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When he opened the Abyss, smoke rose from it like the smoke from a gigantic furnace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30843D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30843D\"></sup> The sun and sky were darkened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30843E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30843E\"></sup> by the smoke from the Abyss.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30843F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30843F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And out of the smoke locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30844G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30844G\"></sup> came down on the earth and were given power like that of scorpions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30844H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30844H\"></sup> of the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They were told not to harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30845I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30845I\"></sup> the grass of the earth or any plant or tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30845J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30845J\"></sup> but only those people who did not have the seal of God on their foreheads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30845K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30845K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They were not allowed to kill them but only to torture them for five months.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30846L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30846L\"></sup> And the agony they suffered was like that of the sting of a scorpion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30846M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30846M\"></sup> when it strikes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>During those days people will seek death but will not find it; they will long to die, but death will elude them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30847N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30847N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The locusts looked like horses prepared for battle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30848O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30848O\"></sup> On their heads they wore something like crowns of gold, and their faces resembled human faces.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30848P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30848P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their hair was like women’s hair, and their teeth were like lions’ teeth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30849Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30849Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They had breastplates like breastplates of iron, and the sound of their wings was like the thundering of many horses and chariots rushing into battle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30850R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30850R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They had tails with stingers, like scorpions, and in their tails they had power to torment people for five months.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30851S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30851S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They had as king over them the angel of the Abyss,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30852T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30852T\"></sup> whose name in Hebrew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30852U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30852U\"></sup> is Abaddon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30852V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30852V\"></sup> and in Greek is Apollyon (that is, Destroyer).",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The first woe is past; two other woes are yet to come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30853W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30853W\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The sixth angel sounded his trumpet, and I heard a voice coming from the four horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30854X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30854X\"></sup> of the golden altar that is before God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30854Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30854Y\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>It said to the sixth angel who had the trumpet, “Release the four angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30855Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30855Z\"></sup> who are bound at the great river Euphrates.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30855AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30855AA\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the four angels who had been kept ready for this very hour and day and month and year were released<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30856AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30856AB\"></sup> to kill a third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30856AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30856AC\"></sup> of mankind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30856AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30856AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The number of the mounted troops was twice ten thousand times ten thousand. I heard their number.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30857AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30857AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The horses and riders I saw in my vision looked like this: Their breastplates were fiery red, dark blue, and yellow as sulfur. The heads of the horses resembled the heads of lions, and out of their mouths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30858AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30858AF\"></sup> came fire, smoke and sulfur.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30858AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30858AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30859AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30859AH\"></sup> of mankind was killed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30859AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30859AI\"></sup> by the three plagues of fire, smoke and sulfur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30859AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30859AJ\"></sup> that came out of their mouths.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The power of the horses was in their mouths and in their tails; for their tails were like snakes, having heads with which they inflict injury.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The rest of mankind who were not killed by these plagues still did not repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30861AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30861AK\"></sup> of the work of their hands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30861AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30861AL\"></sup> they did not stop worshiping demons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30861AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30861AM\"></sup> and idols of gold, silver, bronze, stone and wood—idols that cannot see or hear or walk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30861AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30861AN\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Nor did they repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30862AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30862AO\"></sup> of their murders, their magic arts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30862AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30862AP\"></sup> their sexual immorality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30862AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30862AQ\"></sup> or their thefts."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Then I saw another mighty angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30863A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30863A\"></sup> coming down from heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30863B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30863B\"></sup> He was robed in a cloud, with a rainbow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30863C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30863C\"></sup> above his head; his face was like the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30863D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30863D\"></sup> and his legs were like fiery pillars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30863E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30863E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He was holding a little scroll,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30864F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30864F\"></sup> which lay open in his hand. He planted his right foot on the sea and his left foot on the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30864G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30864G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he gave a loud shout like the roar of a lion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30865H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30865H\"></sup> When he shouted, the voices of the seven thunders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30865I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30865I\"></sup> spoke.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when the seven thunders spoke, I was about to write;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30866J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30866J\"></sup> but I heard a voice from heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30866K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30866K\"></sup> say, “Seal up what the seven thunders have said and do not write it down.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30866L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30866L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel I had seen standing on the sea and on the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30867M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30867M\"></sup> raised his right hand to heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30867N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30867N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30868O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30868O\"></sup> by him who lives for ever and ever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30868P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30868P\"></sup> who created the heavens and all that is in them, the earth and all that is in it, and the sea and all that is in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30868Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30868Q\"></sup> and said, “There will be no more delay!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30868R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30868R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But in the days when the seventh angel is about to sound his trumpet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30869S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30869S\"></sup> the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30869T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30869T\"></sup> of God will be accomplished, just as he announced to his servants the prophets.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30869U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30869U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the voice that I had heard from heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30870V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30870V\"></sup> spoke to me once more: “Go, take the scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30870W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30870W\"></sup> that lies open in the hand of the angel who is standing on the sea and on the land.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So I went to the angel and asked him to give me the little scroll. He said to me, “Take it and eat it. It will turn your stomach sour, but ‘in your mouth it will be as sweet as honey.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30871X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30871X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I took the little scroll from the angel’s hand and ate it. It tasted as sweet as honey in my mouth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30872Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30872Y\"></sup> but when I had eaten it, my stomach turned sour.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I was told, “You must prophesy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30873Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30873Z\"></sup> again about many peoples, nations, languages and kings.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30873AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30873AA\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>I was given a reed like a measuring rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30874A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30874A\"></sup> and was told, “Go and measure the temple of God and the altar, with its worshipers.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But exclude the outer court;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30875B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30875B\"></sup> do not measure it, because it has been given to the Gentiles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30875C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30875C\"></sup> They will trample on the holy city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30875D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30875D\"></sup> for 42 months.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30875E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30875E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I will appoint my two witnesses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30876F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30876F\"></sup> and they will prophesy for 1,260 days,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30876G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30876G\"></sup> clothed in sackcloth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30876H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30876H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They are “the two olive trees”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30877I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30877I\"></sup> and the two lampstands, and “they stand before the Lord of the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30877J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30877J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If anyone tries to harm them, fire comes from their mouths and devours their enemies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30878K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30878K\"></sup> This is how anyone who wants to harm them must die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30878L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30878L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They have power to shut up the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30879M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30879M\"></sup> so that it will not rain during the time they are prophesying;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30879N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30879N\"></sup> and they have power to turn the waters into blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30879O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30879O\"></sup> and to strike the earth with every kind of plague as often as they want.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now when they have finished their testimony, the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30880P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30880P\"></sup> that comes up from the Abyss<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30880Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30880Q\"></sup> will attack them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30880R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30880R\"></sup> and overpower and kill them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their bodies will lie in the public square of the great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30881S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30881S\"></sup>—which is figuratively called Sodom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30881T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30881T\"></sup> and Egypt—where also their Lord was crucified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30881U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30881U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For three and a half days some from every people, tribe, language and nation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30882V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30882V\"></sup> will gaze on their bodies and refuse them burial.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30882W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30882W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The inhabitants of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30883X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30883X\"></sup> will gloat over them and will celebrate by sending each other gifts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30883Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30883Y\"></sup> because these two prophets had tormented those who live on the earth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But after the three and a half days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30884Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30884Z\"></sup> the breath of life from God entered them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30884AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30884AA\"></sup> and they stood on their feet, and terror struck those who saw them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then they heard a loud voice from heaven saying to them, “Come up here.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30885AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30885AB\"></sup> And they went up to heaven in a cloud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30885AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30885AC\"></sup> while their enemies looked on.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>At that very hour there was a severe earthquake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30886AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30886AD\"></sup> and a tenth of the city collapsed. Seven thousand people were killed in the earthquake, and the survivors were terrified and gave glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30886AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30886AE\"></sup> to the God of heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30886AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30886AF\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The second woe has passed; the third woe is coming soon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30887AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30887AG\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The seventh angel sounded his trumpet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30888AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30888AH\"></sup> and there were loud voices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30888AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30888AI\"></sup> in heaven, which said:“The kingdom of the world has becomethe kingdom of our Lord and of his Messiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30888AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30888AJ\"></sup>and he will reign for ever and ever.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30888AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30888AK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the twenty-four elders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30889AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30889AL\"></sup> who were seated on their thrones before God, fell on their faces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30889AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30889AM\"></sup> and worshiped God,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>saying:“We give thanks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30890AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30890AN\"></sup> to you, Lord God Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30890AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30890AO\"></sup>the One who is and who was,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30890AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30890AP\"></sup>because you have taken your great powerand have begun to reign.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30890AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30890AQ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The nations were angry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30891AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30891AR\"></sup>and your wrath has come.The time has come for judging the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30891AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30891AS\"></sup>and for rewarding your servants the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30891AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30891AT\"></sup>and your people who revere your name,both great and small<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30891AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30891AU\"></sup>—and for destroying those who destroy the earth.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then God’s temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30892AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30892AV\"></sup> in heaven was opened, and within his temple was seen the ark of his covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30892AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30892AW\"></sup> And there came flashes of lightning, rumblings, peals of thunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30892AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30892AX\"></sup> an earthquake and a severe hailstorm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30892AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30892AY\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>A great sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30893A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30893A\"></sup> appeared in heaven:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30893B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30893B\"></sup> a woman clothed with the sun, with the moon under her feet and a crown of twelve stars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30893C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30893C\"></sup> on her head.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>She was pregnant and cried out in pain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30894D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30894D\"></sup> as she was about to give birth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then another sign appeared in heaven:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30895E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30895E\"></sup> an enormous red dragon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30895F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30895F\"></sup> with seven heads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30895G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30895G\"></sup> and ten horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30895H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30895H\"></sup> and seven crowns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30895I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30895I\"></sup> on its heads.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Its tail swept a third<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30896J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30896J\"></sup> of the stars out of the sky and flung them to the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30896K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30896K\"></sup> The dragon stood in front of the woman who was about to give birth, so that it might devour her child<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30896L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30896L\"></sup> the moment he was born.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>She gave birth to a son, a male child, who “will rule all the nations with an iron scepter.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30897M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30897M\"></sup> And her child was snatched up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30897N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30897N\"></sup> to God and to his throne.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The woman fled into the wilderness to a place prepared for her by God, where she might be taken care of for 1,260 days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30898O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30898O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then war broke out in heaven. Michael<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30899P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30899P\"></sup> and his angels fought against the dragon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30899Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30899Q\"></sup> and the dragon and his angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30899R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30899R\"></sup> fought back.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But he was not strong enough, and they lost their place in heaven.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The great dragon was hurled down—that ancient serpent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30901S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30901S\"></sup> called the devil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30901T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30901T\"></sup> or Satan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30901U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30901U\"></sup> who leads the whole world astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30901V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30901V\"></sup> He was hurled to the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30901W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30901W\"></sup> and his angels with him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I heard a loud voice in heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30902X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30902X\"></sup> say:“Now have come the salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30902Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30902Y\"></sup> and the powerand the kingdom of our God,and the authority of his Messiah.For the accuser of our brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30902Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30902Z\"></sup>who accuses them before our God day and night,has been hurled down.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They triumphed over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30903AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30903AA\"></sup> himby the blood of the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30903AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30903AB\"></sup>and by the word of their testimony;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30903AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30903AC\"></sup>they did not love their lives so muchas to shrink from death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30903AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30903AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore rejoice, you heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30904AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30904AE\"></sup>and you who dwell in them!But woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30904AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30904AF\"></sup> to the earth and the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30904AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30904AG\"></sup>because the devil has gone down to you!He is filled with fury,because he knows that his time is short.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When the dragon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30905AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30905AH\"></sup> saw that he had been hurled to the earth, he pursued the woman who had given birth to the male child.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30905AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30905AI\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The woman was given the two wings of a great eagle,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30906AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30906AJ\"></sup> so that she might fly to the place prepared for her in the wilderness, where she would be taken care of for a time, times and half a time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30906AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30906AK\"></sup> out of the serpent’s reach.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then from his mouth the serpent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30907AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30907AL\"></sup> spewed water like a river, to overtake the woman and sweep her away with the torrent.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the earth helped the woman by opening its mouth and swallowing the river that the dragon had spewed out of his mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then the dragon was enraged at the woman and went off to wage war<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30909AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30909AM\"></sup> against the rest of her offspring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30909AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30909AN\"></sup>—those who keep God’s commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30909AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30909AO\"></sup> and hold fast their testimony about Jesus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30909AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30909AP\"></sup>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>The dragon stood on the shore of the sea. And I saw a beast coming out of the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30910A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30910A\"></sup> It had ten horns and seven heads,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30910B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30910B\"></sup> with ten crowns on its horns, and on each head a blasphemous name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30910C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30910C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The beast I saw resembled a leopard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30911D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30911D\"></sup> but had feet like those of a bear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30911E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30911E\"></sup> and a mouth like that of a lion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30911F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30911F\"></sup> The dragon gave the beast his power and his throne and great authority.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30911G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30911G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>One of the heads of the beast seemed to have had a fatal wound, but the fatal wound had been healed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30912H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30912H\"></sup> The whole world was filled with wonder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30912I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30912I\"></sup> and followed the beast.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>People worshiped the dragon because he had given authority to the beast, and they also worshiped the beast and asked, “Who is like<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30913J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30913J\"></sup> the beast? Who can wage war against it?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The beast was given a mouth to utter proud words and blasphemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30914K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30914K\"></sup> and to exercise its authority for forty-two months.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30914L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30914L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It opened its mouth to blaspheme God, and to slander his name and his dwelling place and those who live in heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30915M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30915M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It was given power to wage war<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30916N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30916N\"></sup> against God’s holy people and to conquer them. And it was given authority over every tribe, people, language and nation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30916O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30916O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All inhabitants of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30917P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30917P\"></sup> will worship the beast—all whose names have not been written in the Lamb’s book of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30917Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30917Q\"></sup> the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30917R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30917R\"></sup> who was slain from the creation of the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30917S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30917S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever has ears, let them hear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30918T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30918T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“If anyone is to go into captivity,into captivity they will go.If anyone is to be killed with the sword,with the sword they will be killed.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30919U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30919U\"></sup>This calls for patient endurance and faithfulness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30919V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30919V\"></sup> on the part of God’s people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30919W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30919W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I saw a second beast, coming out of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30920X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30920X\"></sup> It had two horns like a lamb, but it spoke like a dragon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30920Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30920Y\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It exercised all the authority<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30921Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30921Z\"></sup> of the first beast on its behalf,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30921AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30921AA\"></sup> and made the earth and its inhabitants worship the first beast,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30921AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30921AB\"></sup> whose fatal wound had been healed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30921AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30921AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And it performed great signs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30922AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30922AD\"></sup> even causing fire to come down from heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30922AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30922AE\"></sup> to the earth in full view of the people.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Because of the signs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30923AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30923AF\"></sup> it was given power to perform on behalf of the first beast, it deceived<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30923AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30923AG\"></sup> the inhabitants of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30923AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30923AH\"></sup> It ordered them to set up an image in honor of the beast who was wounded by the sword and yet lived.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30923AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30923AI\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The second beast was given power to give breath to the image of the first beast, so that the image could speak and cause all who refused to worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30924AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30924AJ\"></sup> the image to be killed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30924AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30924AK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It also forced all people, great and small,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30925AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30925AL\"></sup> rich and poor, free and slave, to receive a mark on their right hands or on their foreheads,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30925AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30925AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>so that they could not buy or sell unless they had the mark,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30926AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30926AN\"></sup> which is the name of the beast or the number of its name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30926AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30926AO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This calls for wisdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30927AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30927AP\"></sup> Let the person who has insight calculate the number of the beast, for it is the number of a man.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30927AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30927AQ\"></sup> That number is 666."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Then I looked, and there before me was the Lamb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30928A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30928A\"></sup> standing on Mount Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30928B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30928B\"></sup> and with him 144,000<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30928C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30928C\"></sup> who had his name and his Father’s name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30928D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30928D\"></sup> written on their foreheads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30928E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30928E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I heard a sound from heaven like the roar of rushing waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30929F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30929F\"></sup> and like a loud peal of thunder.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30929G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30929G\"></sup> The sound I heard was like that of harpists playing their harps.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30929H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they sang a new song<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30930I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30930I\"></sup> before the throne and before the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30930J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30930J\"></sup> and the elders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30930K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30930K\"></sup> No one could learn the song except the 144,000<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30930L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30930L\"></sup> who had been redeemed from the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>These are those who did not defile themselves with women, for they remained virgins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30931M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30931M\"></sup> They follow the Lamb wherever he goes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30931N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30931N\"></sup> They were purchased from among mankind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30931O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30931O\"></sup> and offered as firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30931P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30931P\"></sup> to God and the Lamb.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>No lie was found in their mouths;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30932Q\"></sup> they are blameless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30932R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30932R\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I saw another angel flying in midair,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30933S\"></sup> and he had the eternal gospel to proclaim to those who live on the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30933T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30933T\"></sup>—to every nation, tribe, language and people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30933U\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He said in a loud voice, “Fear God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30934V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30934V\"></sup> and give him glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30934W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30934W\"></sup> because the hour of his judgment has come. Worship him who made<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30934X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30934X\"></sup> the heavens, the earth, the sea and the springs of water.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30934Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30934Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A second angel followed and said, “‘Fallen! Fallen is Babylon the Great,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30935Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30935Z\"></sup> which made all the nations drink the maddening wine of her adulteries.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30935AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30935AA\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A third angel followed them and said in a loud voice: “If anyone worships the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30936AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30936AB\"></sup> and its image<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30936AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30936AC\"></sup> and receives its mark on their forehead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30936AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30936AD\"></sup> or on their hand,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>they, too, will drink the wine of God’s fury,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30937AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30937AE\"></sup> which has been poured full strength into the cup of his wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30937AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30937AF\"></sup> They will be tormented with burning sulfur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30937AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30937AG\"></sup> in the presence of the holy angels and of the Lamb.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the smoke of their torment will rise for ever and ever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30938AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30938AH\"></sup> There will be no rest day or night<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30938AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30938AI\"></sup> for those who worship the beast and its image,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30938AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30938AJ\"></sup> or for anyone who receives the mark of its name.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30938AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30938AK\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This calls for patient endurance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30939AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30939AL\"></sup> on the part of the people of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30939AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30939AM\"></sup> who keep his commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30939AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30939AN\"></sup> and remain faithful to Jesus.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I heard a voice from heaven say, “Write this: Blessed are the dead who die in the Lord<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30940AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30940AO\"></sup> from now on.”“Yes,” says the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30940AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30940AP\"></sup> “they will rest from their labor, for their deeds will follow them.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I looked, and there before me was a white cloud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30941AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30941AQ\"></sup> and seated on the cloud was one like a son of man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30941AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30941AR\"></sup> with a crown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30941AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30941AS\"></sup> of gold on his head and a sharp sickle in his hand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then another angel came out of the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30942AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30942AT\"></sup> and called in a loud voice to him who was sitting on the cloud, “Take your sickle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30942AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30942AU\"></sup> and reap, because the time to reap has come, for the harvest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30942AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30942AV\"></sup> of the earth is ripe.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So he who was seated on the cloud swung his sickle over the earth, and the earth was harvested.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Another angel came out of the temple in heaven, and he too had a sharp sickle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30944AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30944AW\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Still another angel, who had charge of the fire, came from the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30945AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30945AX\"></sup> and called in a loud voice to him who had the sharp sickle, “Take your sharp sickle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30945AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30945AY\"></sup> and gather the clusters of grapes from the earth’s vine, because its grapes are ripe.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The angel swung his sickle on the earth, gathered its grapes and threw them into the great winepress of God’s wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30946AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30946AZ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They were trampled in the winepress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30947BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30947BA\"></sup> outside the city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30947BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30947BB\"></sup> and blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30947BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30947BC\"></sup> flowed out of the press, rising as high as the horses’ bridles for a distance of 1,600 stadia."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>I saw in heaven another great and marvelous sign:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30948A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30948A\"></sup> seven angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30948B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30948B\"></sup> with the seven last plagues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30948C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30948C\"></sup>—last, because with them God’s wrath is completed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw what looked like a sea of glass<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30949D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30949D\"></sup> glowing with fire and, standing beside the sea, those who had been victorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30949E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30949E\"></sup> over the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30949F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30949F\"></sup> and its image<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30949G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30949G\"></sup> and over the number of its name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30949H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30949H\"></sup> They held harps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30949I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30949I\"></sup> given them by God",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and sang the song of God’s servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30950J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30950J\"></sup> Moses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30950K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30950K\"></sup> and of the Lamb:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30950L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30950L\"></sup>“Great and marvelous are your deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30950M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30950M\"></sup>Lord God Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30950N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30950N\"></sup>Just and true are your ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30950O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30950O\"></sup>King of the nations.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who will not fear you, Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30951P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30951P\"></sup>and bring glory to your name?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30951Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30951Q\"></sup>For you alone are holy.All nations will comeand worship before you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30951R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30951R\"></sup>for your righteous acts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30951S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30951S\"></sup> have been revealed.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>After this I looked, and I saw in heaven the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30952T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30952T\"></sup>—that is, the tabernacle of the covenant law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30952U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30952U\"></sup>—and it was opened.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30952V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30952V\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Out of the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30953W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30953W\"></sup> came the seven angels with the seven plagues.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30953X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30953X\"></sup> They were dressed in clean, shining linen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30953Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30953Y\"></sup> and wore golden sashes around their chests.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30953Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30953Z\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then one of the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30954AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30954AA\"></sup> gave to the seven angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30954AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30954AB\"></sup> seven golden bowls filled with the wrath of God, who lives for ever and ever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30954AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30954AC\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the temple was filled with smoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30955AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30955AD\"></sup> from the glory of God and from his power, and no one could enter the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30955AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30955AE\"></sup> until the seven plagues of the seven angels were completed."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then I heard a loud voice from the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30956A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30956A\"></sup> saying to the seven angels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30956B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30956B\"></sup> “Go, pour out the seven bowls of God’s wrath on the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30956C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30956C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The first angel went and poured out his bowl on the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30957D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30957D\"></sup> and ugly, festering sores<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30957E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30957E\"></sup> broke out on the people who had the mark of the beast and worshiped its image.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30957F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30957F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The second angel poured out his bowl on the sea, and it turned into blood like that of a dead person, and every living thing in the sea died.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30958G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30958G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The third angel poured out his bowl on the rivers and springs of water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30959H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30959H\"></sup> and they became blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30959I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30959I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I heard the angel in charge of the waters say:“You are just in these judgments,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30960J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30960J\"></sup> O Holy One,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30960K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30960K\"></sup>you who are and who were;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30960L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30960L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>for they have shed the blood of your holy people and your prophets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30961M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30961M\"></sup>and you have given them blood to drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30961N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30961N\"></sup> as they deserve.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I heard the altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30962O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30962O\"></sup> respond:“Yes, Lord God Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30962P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30962P\"></sup>true and just are your judgments.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30962Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30962Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The fourth angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30963R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30963R\"></sup> poured out his bowl on the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30963S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30963S\"></sup> and the sun was allowed to scorch people with fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30963T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30963T\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They were seared by the intense heat and they cursed the name of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30964U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30964U\"></sup> who had control over these plagues, but they refused to repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30964V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30964V\"></sup> and glorify him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30964W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30964W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The fifth angel poured out his bowl on the throne of the beast,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30965X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30965X\"></sup> and its kingdom was plunged into darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30965Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30965Y\"></sup> People gnawed their tongues in agony",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and cursed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30966Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30966Z\"></sup> the God of heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30966AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30966AA\"></sup> because of their pains and their sores,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30966AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30966AB\"></sup> but they refused to repent of what they had done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30966AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30966AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The sixth angel poured out his bowl on the great river Euphrates,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30967AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30967AD\"></sup> and its water was dried up to prepare the way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30967AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30967AE\"></sup> for the kings from the East.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30967AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30967AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I saw three impure spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30968AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30968AG\"></sup> that looked like frogs;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30968AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30968AH\"></sup> they came out of the mouth of the dragon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30968AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30968AI\"></sup> out of the mouth of the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30968AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30968AJ\"></sup> and out of the mouth of the false prophet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30968AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30968AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They are demonic spirits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30969AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30969AL\"></sup> that perform signs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30969AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30969AM\"></sup> and they go out to the kings of the whole world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30969AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30969AN\"></sup> to gather them for the battle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30969AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30969AO\"></sup> on the great day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30969AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30969AP\"></sup> of God Almighty.",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Look, I come like a thief!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30970AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30970AQ\"></sup> Blessed is the one who stays awake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30970AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30970AR\"></sup> and remains clothed, so as not to go naked and be shamefully exposed.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30970AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30970AS\"></sup></span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then they gathered the kings together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30971AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30971AT\"></sup> to the place that in Hebrew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30971AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30971AU\"></sup> is called Armageddon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30971AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30971AV\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The seventh angel poured out his bowl into the air,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30972AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30972AW\"></sup> and out of the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30972AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30972AX\"></sup> came a loud voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30972AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30972AY\"></sup> from the throne, saying, “It is done!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30972AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30972AZ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then there came flashes of lightning, rumblings, peals of thunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30973BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30973BA\"></sup> and a severe earthquake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30973BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30973BB\"></sup> No earthquake like it has ever occurred since mankind has been on earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30973BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30973BC\"></sup> so tremendous was the quake.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30974BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30974BD\"></sup> split into three parts, and the cities of the nations collapsed. God remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30974BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30974BE\"></sup> Babylon the Great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30974BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30974BF\"></sup> and gave her the cup filled with the wine of the fury of his wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30974BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30974BG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Every island fled away and the mountains could not be found.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30975BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30975BH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>From the sky huge hailstones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30976BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30976BI\"></sup> each weighing about a hundred pounds, fell on people. And they cursed God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30976BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30976BJ\"></sup> on account of the plague of hail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30976BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30976BK\"></sup> because the plague was so terrible."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>One of the seven angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30977A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30977A\"></sup> who had the seven bowls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30977B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30977B\"></sup> came and said to me, “Come, I will show you the punishment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30977C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30977C\"></sup> of the great prostitute,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30977D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30977D\"></sup> who sits by many waters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30977E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30977E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>With her the kings of the earth committed adultery, and the inhabitants of the earth were intoxicated with the wine of her adulteries.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30978F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30978F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the angel carried me away in the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30979G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30979G\"></sup> into a wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30979H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30979H\"></sup> There I saw a woman sitting on a scarlet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30979I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30979I\"></sup> beast that was covered with blasphemous names<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30979J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30979J\"></sup> and had seven heads and ten horns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30979K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30979K\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The woman was dressed in purple and scarlet, and was glittering with gold, precious stones and pearls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30980L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30980L\"></sup> She held a golden cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30980M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30980M\"></sup> in her hand, filled with abominable things and the filth of her adulteries.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30980N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30980N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The name written on her forehead was a mystery:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30981O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30981O\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">babylon the great</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30981P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30981P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the mother of prostitutes</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30981Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30981Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and of the abominations of the earth</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I saw that the woman was drunk with the blood of God’s holy people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30982R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30982R\"></sup> the blood of those who bore testimony to Jesus.When I saw her, I was greatly astonished.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the angel said to me: “Why are you astonished? I will explain to you the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30983S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30983S\"></sup> of the woman and of the beast she rides, which has the seven heads and ten horns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30983T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30983T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The beast, which you saw, once was, now is not, and yet will come up out of the Abyss<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30984U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30984U\"></sup> and go to its destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30984V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30984V\"></sup> The inhabitants of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30984W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30984W\"></sup> whose names have not been written in the book of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30984X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30984X\"></sup> from the creation of the world will be astonished<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30984Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30984Y\"></sup> when they see the beast, because it once was, now is not, and yet will come.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“This calls for a mind with wisdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30985Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30985Z\"></sup> The seven heads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30985AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30985AA\"></sup> are seven hills on which the woman sits.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They are also seven kings. Five have fallen, one is, the other has not yet come; but when he does come, he must remain for only a little while.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The beast who once was, and now is not,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30987AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30987AB\"></sup> is an eighth king. He belongs to the seven and is going to his destruction.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“The ten horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30988AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30988AC\"></sup> you saw are ten kings who have not yet received a kingdom, but who for one hour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30988AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30988AD\"></sup> will receive authority as kings along with the beast.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They have one purpose and will give their power and authority to the beast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30989AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30989AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They will wage war<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30990AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30990AF\"></sup> against the Lamb, but the Lamb will triumph over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30990AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30990AG\"></sup> them because he is Lord of lords and King of kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30990AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30990AH\"></sup>—and with him will be his called, chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30990AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30990AI\"></sup> and faithful followers.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the angel said to me, “The waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30991AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30991AJ\"></sup> you saw, where the prostitute sits, are peoples, multitudes, nations and languages.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30991AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30991AK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The beast and the ten horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30992AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30992AL\"></sup> you saw will hate the prostitute.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30992AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30992AM\"></sup> They will bring her to ruin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30992AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30992AN\"></sup> and leave her naked;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30992AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30992AO\"></sup> they will eat her flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30992AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30992AP\"></sup> and burn her with fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30992AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30992AQ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For God has put it into their hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30993AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30993AR\"></sup> to accomplish his purpose by agreeing to hand over to the beast their royal authority,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30993AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30993AS\"></sup> until God’s words are fulfilled.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30993AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30993AT\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The woman you saw is the great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30994AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30994AU\"></sup> that rules over the kings of the earth.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>After this I saw another angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30995A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30995A\"></sup> coming down from heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30995B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30995B\"></sup> He had great authority, and the earth was illuminated by his splendor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30995C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30995C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>With a mighty voice he shouted:“‘Fallen! Fallen is Babylon the Great!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30996D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30996D\"></sup>She has become a dwelling for demonsand a haunt for every impure spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30996E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30996E\"></sup>a haunt for every unclean bird,a haunt for every unclean and detestable animal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30996F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30996F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For all the nations have drunkthe maddening wine of her adulteries.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30997G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30997G\"></sup>The kings of the earth committed adultery with her,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30997H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30997H\"></sup>and the merchants of the earth grew rich<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30997I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30997I\"></sup> from her excessive luxuries.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30997J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30997J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I heard another voice from heaven say:“‘Come out of her, my people,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30998K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30998K\"></sup>so that you will not share in her sins,so that you will not receive any of her plagues;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30998L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30998L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for her sins are piled up to heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30999M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30999M\"></sup>and God has remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-30999N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-30999N\"></sup> her crimes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Give back to her as she has given;pay her back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31000O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31000O\"></sup> double<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31000P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31000P\"></sup> for what she has done.Pour her a double portion from her own cup.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31000Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31000Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Give her as much torment and griefas the glory and luxury she gave herself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31001R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31001R\"></sup>In her heart she boasts,‘I sit enthroned as queen.I am not a widow;I will never mourn.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31001S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31001S\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore in one day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31002T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31002T\"></sup> her plagues will overtake her:death, mourning and famine.She will be consumed by fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31002U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31002U\"></sup>for mighty is the Lord God who judges her.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“When the kings of the earth who committed adultery with her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31003V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31003V\"></sup> and shared her luxury<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31003W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31003W\"></sup> see the smoke of her burning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31003X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31003X\"></sup> they will weep and mourn over her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31003Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31003Y\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Terrified at her torment, they will stand far off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31004Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31004Z\"></sup> and cry:“‘Woe! Woe to you, great city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31004AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31004AA\"></sup>you mighty city of Babylon!In one hour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31004AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31004AB\"></sup> your doom has come!’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“The merchants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31005AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31005AC\"></sup> of the earth will weep and mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31005AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31005AD\"></sup> over her because no one buys their cargoes anymore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31005AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31005AE\"></sup>—",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>cargoes of gold, silver, precious stones and pearls; fine linen, purple, silk and scarlet cloth; every sort of citron wood, and articles of every kind made of ivory, costly wood, bronze, iron and marble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31006AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31006AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>cargoes of cinnamon and spice, of incense, myrrh and frankincense, of wine and olive oil, of fine flour and wheat; cattle and sheep; horses and carriages; and human beings sold as slaves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31007AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31007AG\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“They will say, ‘The fruit you longed for is gone from you. All your luxury and splendor have vanished, never to be recovered.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The merchants who sold these things and gained their wealth from her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31009AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31009AH\"></sup> will stand far off,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31009AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31009AI\"></sup> terrified at her torment. They will weep and mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31009AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31009AJ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and cry out:“‘Woe! Woe to you, great city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31010AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31010AK\"></sup>dressed in fine linen, purple and scarlet,and glittering with gold, precious stones and pearls!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31010AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31010AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In one hour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31011AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31011AM\"></sup> such great wealth has been brought to ruin!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31011AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31011AN\"></sup>“Every sea captain, and all who travel by ship, the sailors, and all who earn their living from the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31011AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31011AO\"></sup> will stand far off.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31011AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31011AP\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When they see the smoke of her burning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31012AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31012AQ\"></sup> they will exclaim, ‘Was there ever a city like this great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31012AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31012AR\"></sup>?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31012AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31012AS\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will throw dust on their heads,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31013AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31013AT\"></sup> and with weeping and mourning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31013AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31013AU\"></sup> cry out:“‘Woe! Woe to you, great city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31013AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31013AV\"></sup>where all who had ships on the seabecame rich through her wealth!In one hour she has been brought to ruin!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31013AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31013AW\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Rejoice over her, you heavens!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31014AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31014AX\"></sup>Rejoice, you people of God!Rejoice, apostles and prophets!For God has judged herwith the judgment she imposed on you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31014AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31014AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then a mighty angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31015AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31015AZ\"></sup> picked up a boulder the size of a large millstone and threw it into the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31015BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31015BA\"></sup> and said:“With such violencethe great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31015BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31015BB\"></sup> of Babylon will be thrown down,never to be found again.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The music of harpists and musicians, pipers and trumpeters,will never be heard in you again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31016BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31016BC\"></sup>No worker of any tradewill ever be found in you again.The sound of a millstonewill never be heard in you again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31016BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31016BD\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The light of a lampwill never shine in you again.The voice of bridegroom and bridewill never be heard in you again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31017BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31017BE\"></sup>Your merchants were the world’s important people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31017BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31017BF\"></sup>By your magic spell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31017BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31017BG\"></sup> all the nations were led astray.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In her was found the blood of prophets and of God’s holy people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31018BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31018BH\"></sup>of all who have been slaughtered on the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31018BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31018BI\"></sup>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>After this I heard what sounded like the roar of a great multitude<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31019A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31019A\"></sup> in heaven shouting:“Hallelujah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31019B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31019B\"></sup>Salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31019C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31019C\"></sup> and glory and power<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31019D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31019D\"></sup> belong to our God,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>for true and just are his judgments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31020E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31020E\"></sup>He has condemned the great prostitute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31020F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31020F\"></sup>who corrupted the earth by her adulteries.He has avenged on her the blood of his servants.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31020G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31020G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And again they shouted:“Hallelujah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31021H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31021H\"></sup>The smoke from her goes up for ever and ever.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31021I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31021I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The twenty-four elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31022J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31022J\"></sup> and the four living creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31022K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31022K\"></sup> fell down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31022L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31022L\"></sup> and worshiped God, who was seated on the throne. And they cried:“Amen, Hallelujah!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31022M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31022M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then a voice came from the throne, saying:“Praise our God,all you his servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31023N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31023N\"></sup>you who fear him,both great and small!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31023O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31023O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I heard what sounded like a great multitude,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31024P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31024P\"></sup> like the roar of rushing waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31024Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31024Q\"></sup> and like loud peals of thunder, shouting:“Hallelujah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31024R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31024R\"></sup>For our Lord God Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31024S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31024S\"></sup> reigns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31024T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31024T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Let us rejoice and be gladand give him glory!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31025U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31025U\"></sup>For the wedding of the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31025V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31025V\"></sup> has come,and his bride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31025W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31025W\"></sup> has made herself ready.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Fine linen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31026X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31026X\"></sup> bright and clean,was given her to wear.”(Fine linen stands for the righteous acts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31026Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31026Y\"></sup> of God’s holy people.)",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the angel said to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31027Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31027Z\"></sup> “Write this:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31027AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31027AA\"></sup> Blessed are those who are invited to the wedding supper of the Lamb!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31027AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31027AB\"></sup> And he added, “These are the true words of God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31027AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31027AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>At this I fell at his feet to worship him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31028AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31028AD\"></sup> But he said to me, “Don’t do that! I am a fellow servant with you and with your brothers and sisters who hold to the testimony of Jesus. Worship God!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31028AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31028AE\"></sup> For it is the Spirit of prophecy who bears testimony to Jesus.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31028AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31028AF\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I saw heaven standing open<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31029AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31029AG\"></sup> and there before me was a white horse, whose rider<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31029AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31029AH\"></sup> is called Faithful and True.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31029AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31029AI\"></sup> With justice he judges and wages war.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31029AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31029AJ\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His eyes are like blazing fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31030AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31030AK\"></sup> and on his head are many crowns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31030AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31030AL\"></sup> He has a name written on him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31030AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31030AM\"></sup> that no one knows but he himself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31030AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31030AN\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He is dressed in a robe dipped in blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31031AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31031AO\"></sup> and his name is the Word of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31031AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31031AP\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The armies of heaven were following him, riding on white horses and dressed in fine linen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31032AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31032AQ\"></sup> white<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31032AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31032AR\"></sup> and clean.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Coming out of his mouth is a sharp sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31033AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31033AS\"></sup> with which to strike down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31033AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31033AT\"></sup> the nations. “He will rule them with an iron scepter.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31033AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31033AU\"></sup> He treads the winepress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31033AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31033AV\"></sup> of the fury of the wrath of God Almighty.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>On his robe and on his thigh he has this name written:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31034AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31034AW\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">king of kings and lord of lords</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31034AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31034AX\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And I saw an angel standing in the sun, who cried in a loud voice to all the birds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31035AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31035AY\"></sup> flying in midair,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31035AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31035AZ\"></sup> “Come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31035BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31035BA\"></sup> gather together for the great supper of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31035BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31035BB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>so that you may eat the flesh of kings, generals, and the mighty, of horses and their riders, and the flesh of all people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31036BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31036BC\"></sup> free and slave,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31036BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31036BD\"></sup> great and small.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31036BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31036BE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then I saw the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31037BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31037BF\"></sup> and the kings of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31037BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31037BG\"></sup> and their armies gathered together to wage war against the rider on the horse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31037BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31037BH\"></sup> and his army.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But the beast was captured, and with it the false prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BI\"></sup> who had performed the signs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BJ\"></sup> on its behalf.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BK\"></sup> With these signs he had deluded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BL\"></sup> those who had received the mark of the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BM\"></sup> and worshiped its image.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BN\"></sup> The two of them were thrown alive into the fiery lake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BO\"></sup> of burning sulfur.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31038BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31038BP\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The rest were killed with the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31039BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31039BQ\"></sup> coming out of the mouth of the rider on the horse,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31039BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31039BR\"></sup> and all the birds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31039BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31039BS\"></sup> gorged themselves on their flesh."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>And I saw an angel coming down out of heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31040A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31040A\"></sup> having the key<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31040B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31040B\"></sup> to the Abyss<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31040C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31040C\"></sup> and holding in his hand a great chain.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He seized the dragon, that ancient serpent, who is the devil, or Satan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31041D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31041D\"></sup> and bound him for a thousand years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31041E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31041E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He threw him into the Abyss,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31042F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31042F\"></sup> and locked and sealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31042G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31042G\"></sup> it over him, to keep him from deceiving the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31042H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31042H\"></sup> anymore until the thousand years were ended. After that, he must be set free for a short time.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I saw thrones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043I\"></sup> on which were seated those who had been given authority to judge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043J\"></sup> And I saw the souls of those who had been beheaded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043K\"></sup> because of their testimony about Jesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043L\"></sup> and because of the word of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043M\"></sup> They had not worshiped the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043N\"></sup> or its image and had not received its mark on their foreheads or their hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043O\"></sup> They came to life and reigned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31043P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31043P\"></sup> with Christ a thousand years.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>(The rest of the dead did not come to life until the thousand years were ended.) This is the first resurrection.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31044Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31044Q\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31045R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31045R\"></sup> and holy are those who share in the first resurrection. The second death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31045S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31045S\"></sup> has no power over them, but they will be priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31045T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31045T\"></sup> of God and of Christ and will reign with him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31045U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31045U\"></sup> for a thousand years.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the thousand years are over,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31046V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31046V\"></sup> Satan will be released from his prison",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and will go out to deceive the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31047W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31047W\"></sup> in the four corners of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31047X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31047X\"></sup>—Gog and Magog<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31047Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31047Y\"></sup>—and to gather them for battle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31047Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31047Z\"></sup> In number they are like the sand on the seashore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31047AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31047AA\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They marched across the breadth of the earth and surrounded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31048AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31048AB\"></sup> the camp of God’s people, the city he loves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31048AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31048AC\"></sup> But fire came down from heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31048AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31048AD\"></sup> and devoured them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the devil, who deceived them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31049AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31049AE\"></sup> was thrown into the lake of burning sulfur,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31049AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31049AF\"></sup> where the beast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31049AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31049AG\"></sup> and the false prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31049AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31049AH\"></sup> had been thrown. They will be tormented day and night for ever and ever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31049AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31049AI\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I saw a great white throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31050AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31050AJ\"></sup> and him who was seated on it. The earth and the heavens fled from his presence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31050AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31050AK\"></sup> and there was no place for them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I saw the dead, great and small,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31051AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31051AL\"></sup> standing before the throne, and books were opened.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31051AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31051AM\"></sup> Another book was opened, which is the book of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31051AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31051AN\"></sup> The dead were judged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31051AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31051AO\"></sup> according to what they had done<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31051AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31051AP\"></sup> as recorded in the books.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The sea gave up the dead that were in it, and death and Hades<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31052AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31052AQ\"></sup> gave up the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31052AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31052AR\"></sup> that were in them, and each person was judged according to what they had done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31052AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31052AS\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31053AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31053AT\"></sup> and Hades<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31053AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31053AU\"></sup> were thrown into the lake of fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31053AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31053AV\"></sup> The lake of fire is the second death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31053AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31053AW\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Anyone whose name was not found written in the book of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31054AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31054AX\"></sup> was thrown into the lake of fire."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>Then I saw “a new heaven and a new earth,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31055A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31055A\"></sup> for the first heaven and the first earth had passed away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31055B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31055B\"></sup> and there was no longer any sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I saw the Holy City,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31056C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31056C\"></sup> the new Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31056D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31056D\"></sup> prepared as a bride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31056E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31056E\"></sup> beautifully dressed for her husband.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I heard a loud voice from the throne saying, “Look! God’s dwelling place is now among the people, and he will dwell with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31057F\"></sup> They will be his people, and God himself will be with them and be their God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31057G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31057G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘He will wipe every tear from their eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31058H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31058H\"></sup> There will be no more death’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31058I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31058I\"></sup> or mourning or crying or pain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31058J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31058J\"></sup> for the old order of things has passed away.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31058K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31058K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who was seated on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31059L\"></sup> said, “I am making everything new!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31059M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31059M\"></sup> Then he said, “Write this down, for these words are trustworthy and true.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31059N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31059N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said to me: “It is done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31060O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31060O\"></sup> I am the Alpha and the Omega,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31060P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31060P\"></sup> the Beginning and the End. To the thirsty I will give water without cost<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31060Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31060Q\"></sup> from the spring of the water of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31060R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31060R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Those who are victorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31061S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31061S\"></sup> will inherit all this, and I will be their God and they will be my children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31061T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31061T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the cowardly, the unbelieving, the vile, the murderers, the sexually immoral, those who practice magic arts, the idolaters and all liars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31062U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31062U\"></sup>—they will be consigned to the fiery lake of burning sulfur.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31062V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31062V\"></sup> This is the second death.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31062W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31062W\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>One of the seven angels who had the seven bowls full of the seven last plagues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31063X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31063X\"></sup> came and said to me, “Come, I will show you the bride,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31063Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31063Y\"></sup> the wife of the Lamb.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he carried me away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31064Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31064Z\"></sup> in the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31064AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31064AA\"></sup> to a mountain great and high, and showed me the Holy City, Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31064AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31064AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It shone with the glory of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31065AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31065AC\"></sup> and its brilliance was like that of a very precious jewel, like a jasper,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31065AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31065AD\"></sup> clear as crystal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31065AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31065AE\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It had a great, high wall with twelve gates,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31066AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31066AF\"></sup> and with twelve angels at the gates. On the gates were written the names of the twelve tribes of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31066AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31066AG\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There were three gates on the east, three on the north, three on the south and three on the west.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The wall of the city had twelve foundations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31068AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31068AH\"></sup> and on them were the names of the twelve apostles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31068AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31068AI\"></sup> of the Lamb.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The angel who talked with me had a measuring rod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31069AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31069AJ\"></sup> of gold to measure the city, its gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31069AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31069AK\"></sup> and its walls.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The city was laid out like a square, as long as it was wide. He measured the city with the rod and found it to be 12,000 stadia in length, and as wide and high as it is long.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The angel measured the wall using human<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31071AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31071AL\"></sup> measurement, and it was 144 cubits thick.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wall was made of jasper,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31072AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31072AM\"></sup> and the city of pure gold, as pure as glass.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31072AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31072AN\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The foundations of the city walls were decorated with every kind of precious stone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31073AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31073AO\"></sup> The first foundation was jasper,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31073AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31073AP\"></sup> the second sapphire, the third agate, the fourth emerald,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>the fifth onyx, the sixth ruby,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31074AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31074AQ\"></sup> the seventh chrysolite, the eighth beryl, the ninth topaz, the tenth turquoise, the eleventh jacinth, and the twelfth amethyst.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The twelve gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31075AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31075AR\"></sup> were twelve pearls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31075AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31075AS\"></sup> each gate made of a single pearl. The great street of the city was of gold, as pure as transparent glass.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31075AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31075AT\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I did not see a temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31076AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31076AU\"></sup> in the city, because the Lord God Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31076AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31076AV\"></sup> and the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31076AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31076AW\"></sup> are its temple.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The city does not need the sun or the moon to shine on it, for the glory of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31077AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31077AX\"></sup> gives it light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31077AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31077AY\"></sup> and the Lamb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31077AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31077AZ\"></sup> is its lamp.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The nations will walk by its light, and the kings of the earth will bring their splendor into it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31078BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31078BA\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>On no day will its gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31079BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31079BB\"></sup> ever be shut,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31079BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31079BC\"></sup> for there will be no night there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31079BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31079BD\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The glory and honor of the nations will be brought into it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31080BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31080BE\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Nothing impure will ever enter it, nor will anyone who does what is shameful or deceitful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31081BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31081BF\"></sup> but only those whose names are written in the Lamb’s book of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31081BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31081BG\"></sup>"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then the angel showed me the river<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31082A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31082A\"></sup> of the water of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31082B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31082B\"></sup> as clear as crystal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31082C\"></sup> flowing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31082D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31082D\"></sup> from the throne of God and of the Lamb",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>down the middle of the great street of the city. On each side of the river stood the tree of life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31083E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31083E\"></sup> bearing twelve crops of fruit, yielding its fruit every month. And the leaves of the tree are for the healing of the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31083F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31083F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>No longer will there be any curse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31084G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31084G\"></sup> The throne of God and of the Lamb will be in the city, and his servants will serve him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31084H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31084H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will see his face,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31085I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31085I\"></sup> and his name will be on their foreheads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31085J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31085J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>There will be no more night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31086K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31086K\"></sup> They will not need the light of a lamp or the light of the sun, for the Lord God will give them light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31086L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31086L\"></sup> And they will reign for ever and ever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31086M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31086M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The angel said to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31087N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31087N\"></sup> “These words are trustworthy and true.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31087O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31087O\"></sup> The Lord, the God who inspires the prophets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31087P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31087P\"></sup> sent his angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31087Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31087Q\"></sup> to show his servants the things that must soon take place.”",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Look, I am coming soon!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31088R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31088R\"></sup> Blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31088S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31088S\"></sup> is the one who keeps the words of the prophecy written in this scroll.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31088T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31088T\"></sup></span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I, John, am the one who heard and saw these things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31089U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31089U\"></sup> And when I had heard and seen them, I fell down to worship at the feet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31089V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31089V\"></sup> of the angel who had been showing them to me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But he said to me, “Don’t do that! I am a fellow servant with you and with your fellow prophets and with all who keep the words of this scroll.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31090W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31090W\"></sup> Worship God!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31090X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31090X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then he told me, “Do not seal up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31091Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31091Y\"></sup> the words of the prophecy of this scroll,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31091Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31091Z\"></sup> because the time is near.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31091AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31091AA\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let the one who does wrong continue to do wrong; let the vile person continue to be vile; let the one who does right continue to do right; and let the holy person continue to be holy.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31092AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31092AB\"></sup>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Look, I am coming soon!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31093AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31093AC\"></sup> My reward is with me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31093AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31093AD\"></sup> and I will give to each person according to what they have done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31093AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31093AE\"></sup></span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am the Alpha and the Omega,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31094AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31094AF\"></sup> the First and the Last,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31094AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31094AG\"></sup> the Beginning and the End.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31094AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31094AH\"></sup></span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Blessed are those who wash their robes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31095AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31095AI\"></sup> that they may have the right to the tree of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31095AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31095AJ\"></sup> and may go through the gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31095AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31095AK\"></sup> into the city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31095AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31095AL\"></sup></span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Outside<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31096AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31096AM\"></sup> are the dogs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31096AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31096AN\"></sup> those who practice magic arts, the sexually immoral, the murderers, the idolaters and everyone who loves and practices falsehood.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I, Jesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31097AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31097AO\"></sup> have sent my angel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31097AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31097AP\"></sup> to give you this testimony for the churches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31097AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31097AQ\"></sup> I am the Root<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31097AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31097AR\"></sup> and the Offspring of David,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31097AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31097AS\"></sup> and the bright Morning Star.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31097AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31097AT\"></sup></span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31098AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31098AU\"></sup> and the bride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31098AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31098AV\"></sup> say, “Come!” And let the one who hears say, “Come!” Let the one who is thirsty come; and let the one who wishes take the free gift of the water of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31098AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31098AW\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I warn everyone who hears the words of the prophecy of this scroll:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31099AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31099AX\"></sup> If anyone adds anything to them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31099AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31099AY\"></sup> God will add to that person the plagues described in this scroll.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31099AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31099AZ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And if anyone takes words away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31100BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31100BA\"></sup> from this scroll of prophecy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31100BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31100BB\"></sup> God will take away from that person any share in the tree of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31100BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31100BC\"></sup> and in the Holy City, which are described in this scroll.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who testifies to these things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31101BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31101BD\"></sup> says, <span class=\"woj\">“Yes, I am coming soon.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31101BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31101BE\"></sup></span>Amen. Come, Lord Jesus.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31101BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31101BF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus be with God’s people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-31102BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-31102BG\"></sup> Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;